<script>
  $(document).ready(function () {
    const $carouselTrack = $(".carousel-track");
    const $prevButton = $(".carousel-control.prev");
    const $nextButton = $(".carousel-control.next");
    const $carouselItems = $(".carousel-item");
    const totalItems = $carouselItems.length;
    let currentIndex = 0;
    let slidesToShow = 3.5; // Default value
    // Function to calculate slides to show based on screen width
    const calculateSlidesToShow = (width) => {
      if (width < 640) return 1; // Mobile
      if (width < 1024) return 2.5; // Tablet
      if (width < 1440) return 3.5; // Medium screens
      return 4.5; // Large screens
    };
    // Function to update slidesToShow on resize
    const updateSlidesToShow = () => {
      slidesToShow = calculateSlidesToShow($(window).width());
      $carouselItems.css("flex", `0 0 calc(100% / ${slidesToShow})`);
      updateCarousel();
    };
    // Function to update the carousel position
    const updateCarousel = () => {
      const translateX = -currentIndex * (100 / slidesToShow);
      $carouselTrack.css("transform", `translateX(${translateX}%)`);
      // Handle button visibility
      if (currentIndex === 0) {
        $prevButton.addClass("disabled").hide();
      } else {
        $prevButton.removeClass("disabled").show();
      }
      if (currentIndex >= totalItems - slidesToShow) {
        $nextButton.addClass("disabled").hide();
      } else {
        $nextButton.removeClass("disabled").show();
      }
    };
    // Next button click
    $nextButton.click(() => {
      if (currentIndex < totalItems - slidesToShow) {
        currentIndex++;
        updateCarousel();
      }
    });
    // Previous button click
    $prevButton.click(() => {
      if (currentIndex > 0) {
        currentIndex--;
        updateCarousel();
      }
    });
    // Initialize carousel and handle window resize
    updateSlidesToShow();
    $(window).resize(updateSlidesToShow);
    // Initialize carousel visibility
    updateCarousel();
  });
</script>

  /* General Button Styling */
.button-container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
.responsive-button {
  display: inline-block;
  padding:10px 20px;
  border: 2px solid #5FC958;
  background-color: #00000;
  color: #5FC958;
  text-align: center;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 30px;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 2;
  min-width: 120px;
 outline: none;
  font-family: Poppins;
  font-weight: 600;
}
  .responsive-button:hover{
 background-color: #EAFCEF;
    color: #5FC958;
}
     .active {
  background-color: #5FC958;
  color: white;
}           
/* Hide dropdown container by default */
.dropdown-container {
  display: none;
}
@media (max-width: 1320px) {
.responsive-button {
  padding:10px 20px;
  min-width: 110px;
}
}
  @media (max-width: 1220px) {
.responsive-button {
  padding:10px 20px;
  min-width: 90px;
}
}
@media (max-width: 1050px) {
.responsive-button {
  padding:10px 20px;
  min-width: 70px;
}
} 
/* Media Query for Mobile Devices */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  /* Hide the button row and show the dropdown */
  .button-container {
    display: none;
  } 
  .dropdown-container {
    display: block;
  }
  #mobile-dropdown {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    font-size: 16px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
  }
   #mobile-dropdown:hover {
    border: 2px solid #5FC958;
  }
  select {
	-webkit-appearance: none;
	-moz-appearance: none;
	appearance: none;
	background: url(images/chevron-down.svg) no-repeat center / contain;
	background-size: 20px;
	background-position: calc(100% - 10px);
}
}

  }
